com.coveringarray.parsers

Class CoveringArrayParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveringarray.parsers.CoveringArrayParser

  • public class CoveringArrayParser
extends Object
    A Parser for covering arrays that can be used to extract the parameters and the array.

    Supported types are:-

    Colbourn Arrays CA(N;t,k,v).txt
    NIST Arraysca.t.v^t.txt
    Torres-Jimenez ArraysN[no]k[no]v[no]^t[no].ca
    Non-Standard Arrayst_k_v.txt

    The class makes a best effort detection for unsupported arrays also.
